<plot>Based on true events, "Turtle" is the story of Toby and Melissa, best friends who for the past two years have shared their most private thoughts and secrets. Except for one. Melissa has been hiding her terminal illness from Toby to spare him the pain. With her time running short, she breaks the news and they spend their last days together reminding each other of just how special their relationship is.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?621421</url></doc>
